description: SecurityHandling:  Records security handling parameters for cells in a radio access network at a specific point in time.  dateTime: Timestamp of the record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Duplicate of CellId; Id3:  Arbitrary ID (likely redundant); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; SecurityHandling.integrityProtectAlgoPrio: Priority of integrity protection algorithm; SecurityHandling.personalDataProtectionEnabled: Flag indicating personal data protection; SecurityHandling.securityHandlingId: Security handling instance ID; SecurityHandling.cipheringAlgoPrio: Priority of ciphering algorithm; SecurityHandling.integProtUserPlaneLowRate: Handling of integrity protection for low-rate user plane; SecurityHandling.featCtrlIntegProtUserPlane: Feature control for integrity protection in user plane; SecurityHandling.rbIdSupervisionActive: Flag for RB ID supervision; SecurityHandling.countWrapSupervisionActive: Flag for count wrap supervision.
